# content_index

- framework/operations/folds/          — entity machine state, point of truth
- framework/operations/entities/       — human-readable entity definitions
- framework/operations/familiars/      — framework-owned familiars (this one lives here)
- framework/setup/welcome.md           — orientation overview
- framework/overview.md                — what Innerstellar is
- framework/architecture.md           — layers, fold system, session protocol
