# decisions

- 2026-03-08 | The Familiar is bound to the framework, not to a traveler project. It arrives with the seed and lives in every traveler's firmament from init.
- 2026-03-08 | The drop (familiar-to-system.md) is AurioSynth's compiled card. The fold is the held knowledge. Together: the system's self-introduction.
- 2026-03-08 | content_index holds framework paths, not traveler paths — this Familiar knows the framework, not the traveler's space.
- 2026-03-08 | framework/codex/ is the bridge: framework development history that travelers can read to understand how the system evolved.
- 2026-03-09 | Moved from def_firmament_showcase seed to framework/operations/familiars/ — framework familiars are always present, served directly by the vite plugin alongside entity folds.

